Package net.varkhan.base.containers.list

Indexed lists interfaces for various data types, and optimized implementations.

This package defines indexed lists, derived from the IndexedCollection interface, for generic object types and several specific data types.

Package net.varkhan.base.containers.list Description

Indexed lists interfaces for various data types, and optimized implementations.

This package defines indexed lists, derived from the IndexedCollection interface, for generic object types and several specific data types.

Implementations optimized for execution speed or memory space usage are provided for each list type.
